{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=222f83ebfb29b3c365863ae71162857e&src=http%3A%2F%2Fa.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F00e93901213fb80ea33ccafb3ed12f2eb9389429.jpg","summary":"安徽黄梅戏艺术职业学院，简称安戏院。坐落于安徽省安庆市宜秀区大龙山镇，是面向全国招生的以培养黄梅戏表演艺术人才为主的高职院校。1956年，安庆市黄梅戏剧团演员训练班创建。1958年，安庆市黄梅戏剧团演员训练班更名为安庆市艺术学校。1963年，安庆市艺术学校更名为安徽安庆黄梅戏学校。1976年，安徽安庆黄梅戏学校复校并改建为安庆市黄梅戏剧团演员训练班。2011年，安徽黄梅戏学校升格为安徽黄梅戏艺术职业学院。安徽黄梅戏艺术职业学院有表演系、音乐系、综艺系、美术系、舞蹈系五大系。","tags":["艺术类","专科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1958","所在地区":"安徽省安庆市宜秀区北部新城","院校隶属":"安徽省教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=573de05450bb6e2223d40ea81616eed2&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3686946471%2C967197902%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=9a96b346897d3eaf8dcb027adc75f836&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3603598470%2C4002816130%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=e6efead9cde3b4184099b44bb5e670b3&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3740707123%2C1055638527%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=2c4266efd4723b8b39f56d34ec94df7c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3437633929%2C3855661434%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=456901d9fd50ae546f66ee090b851875&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3655249558%2C1016437032%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534499601&di=90ae55fd33fb7db5e5b6f07e